==English==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{m|enm|abaishment}}, from {{etyl|frm|en}} {{m|frm|abaissement||astonishment}} alteration of {{m|frm|esbaissement}}, from {{m|frm|esbaiss}} + {{m|frm|-ment}}.<ref>{{R:MW3 1976|page=2}}</ref>
* Compare French ''[[ébahissement]]''

